data.description: Motivated Seller, Bring all offers! Adorable Ranch in the heart of SE Raleigh. Open concept living room with high ceilings and a gas fireplace opening into an eat-in kitchen with stainless appliances and an island. Cute patio area in the back is great to grill and entertain. Updated hardwoods in several rooms, updated roof approx. 3 years old. 1 car garage. Don't miss out on this gem!
